_sText:
Zm_stab_plateaus_v3

made by Stabhappyjim (stabby@zmmapperz.net)

Features
- around 40 spawns
- Barricade spot
- jumping/climbing/camping spots
- 2 secrets

A small map good for zombie infection (reload) servers
set in a misty swamp humans have to jump up rocks to get onto higher ground
away from the zombies.

good for around 20-32 players. Mostly jumping spots 
like in cratesfinal, but also a castle for barricading

i hope you like this map, if you do please leave a comment =)

included: .bsp map for gameserver, bzipped map for downloadserver

visit our zombiemod servers/mapping community at 
http://www.zmmapperz.net

for more maps by our members
